languages.text: "Дружочки в мой голове просто сходят с ума от восторга. В дверку то и дело стучатся гости с той стороны, желая поделиться своими предсмертными видениями. В очередь вы, идиоты! Я одна, а вас вон сколько!"

languages.text: "The little whisperers in my head are going crazy with excitement. Lots of knocking on the door. All the visitors from the other side who can't wait to share the last visions they had before they died. Oi, form an orderly queue, idiots! There's a load of you and only one of me!"

languages.text: «Los susurros que oigo en mi cabeza están muy agitados. Están llamando constantemente a mi puerta. Son visitantes del otro lado, que están deseando revelarme lo que vieron justo antes de morir. ¡Eh, de uno en uno, idiotas! ¡Que sois un montón y yo solo una!».
languages.original_text: "The little whisperers in my head are going crazy with excitement. Lots of knocking on the door. languages.text: 「あたいの頭の中でささやく小さな者たちが興奮して暴れ回っている。扉を叩きまくる音がする。あの世からの訪問者たちが、死ぬ前に見た最後の光景をあたいと分かち合いたくてウズウズしているようね。ちょっと、ちゃんと並びなさいよ、このマヌケども！アンタたちは大勢いるけど、あたいは一人なんだからね！」
languages.original_text: "The little whisperers in my head are going crazy with excitement. Lots of knocking on the door. All the visitors from the other side who can't wait to share the last visions they had before they died. Oi, form an orderly queue, idiots! There's a load of you and only one of me!"

languages.text: “我脑内的低语声兴奋得快发疯了。来自另一边的访客不停敲门，迫不及待地打算分享他们死前看到的最后一幕。喂，你们这群白痴，都给我排好队！你们有一大堆人，可我只有一个！”
languages.original_text: "The little whisperers in my head are going crazy with excitement. Lots of knocking on the door. All the visitors from the other side who can't wait to share the last visions they had before they died. Oi, form an orderly queue, idiots! There's a load of you and only one of me!"

languages.text: « Les petites voix dans ma tête sont folles d'excitation. Ça toque beaucoup à la porte. Tous les visiteurs de l'autre côté qui ont hâte de partager ce qu'ils ont vu avant de mourir... Oh, faites la queue, bande d'idiots ! Vous êtes beaucoup plus nombreux que moi ! »
languages.original_text: "The little whisperers in my head are going crazy with excitement. Lots of knocking on the door. All the visitors from the other side who can't wait to share the last visions they had before they died. Oi, form an orderly queue, idiots! There's a load of you and only one of me!"

languages.text: "Die kleinen Flüsterer in meinem Kopf drehen vor Aufregung durch. An allen Türen klopft es. Alles Besucher von der anderen Seite, die es nicht länger erwarten können, die letzten Momente vor ihrem Tod zu teilen. Oi, steht in geordneter Reihe, ihr Idioten! Es gibt eine Unmenge von Euch, mich gibt es nur einmal!"

languages.text: "Kafamın içindeki minik fısıldayanlarım, heyecandan çılgına döndü. Kapıya vurup duruyorlar. Diğer taraftaki ziyaretçiler, ölmeden önceki son görülerini paylaşmak için yerinde duramıyor. Of, düzgünce sıranızı beklesenize ahmaklar! Siz ziyadesiyle kalabalıksınız, bense tek kişiyim!"
languages.original_text: "The little whisperers in my head are going crazy with excitement. Lots of knocking on the door. All the visitors from the other side who can't wait to share the last visions they had before they died. Oi, form an orderly queue, idiots! There's a load of you and only one of me!"

traits.locale_text: "Kafamın içindeki minik fısıltılar, heyecandan çılgına döndü. Sürekli kapıya vurup duruyorlar. Diğer taraftaki ziyaretçiler, ölmeden önceki son görülerini paylaşmak için sabırsızlanıyorlar. Oy, düzgünce sıranızı bekleyin ahmaklar! Siz ziyadesiyle kalabalıksınız, bense tek kişiyim!"
